OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FEighty years since families
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fleft 'ghost village'       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Eighty years has passed since families 
OL,6, were evicted from a small village on   
OL,7, Salisbury Plain.                       
OL,9,FIn 1943, 150 people living in Imber    
OL,10,Fwere asked to move out so that the     
OL,11,Fvillage could be turned into a military
OL,12,Ftraining area.                         
OL,14,FThe letters were handed to villagers on
OL,15,F1 November 1943 and they had to leave  
OL,16,Ftheir homes by 17 December.            
OL,18,FThe residents were promised they could 
OL,19,Freturn to their homes after the war -  
OL,20,Fbut that never happened.               
